videos.description: Kendric Davis sends a nice, no-look bounce pass to Isiaha Mike in transition for an early slam vs. Houston.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Davis' no-look dish to Mike sets up an early SMU jam) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Davis' no-look dish to Mike sets up an early SMU jam

videos.description: Isiaha Mike takes advantage of another Houston turnover, sending a lob up to the rim for Feron Hunt who throws it down.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Houston turnover leads to SMU alley-oop) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Houston turnover leads to SMU alley-oop

videos.description: Kendric Davis crosses up his Houston defender and makes a stepback jumper look easy.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (SMU's Davis channels Kemba on slick stepback) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: SMU's Davis channels Kemba on slick stepback

videos.description: Kendric Davis fires a long pass from the SMU logo to the rim for a cutting Feron Hunt who finishes the slam late in the first half vs. Houston.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Davis sends an alley-oop lob from the logo) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Davis sends an alley-oop lob from the logo

videos.description: Tyson Jolly rises to the rim, reaches back to catch CJ White's miss and throws down a powerful two-handed putback slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (SMU's Jolly reaches back and throws down a monster slam) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: SMU's Jolly reaches back and throws down a monster slam

videos.description: Feron Hunt flushes home another slam for SMU, this time rushing in from the corner to attack the rim against Houston.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hunt races in from the corner for SMU jam) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Hunt races in from the corner for SMU jam

videos.description: Caleb Mills drives into the lane and drains a tough basket in the final minute of the second half to pull Houston within three of SMU, eventually forcing overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mills' acrobatic shot sets up OT for Houston vs. SMU) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Mills' acrobatic shot sets up OT for Houston vs. SMU
